      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity for someone seeking simple, practical transportation without the premium price tag. This vehicle shows its age, but it remains a straightforward value buy with solid everyday usefulness for the right owner. Ideal as an inexpensive commuter, backup vehicle, or starter car for a hands-on buyer looking to get the most for their money.",
